        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 18:18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and its constr. מדיני once, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 19:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Everywhere else the text has מדונים, for which the Kerı̂ has מדינים, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 18:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
